docs.abstract: Officials are looking for signs of manipulation behind the recent market frenzy.

docs.lead_paragraph: Keith Gill’s cheerleading of GameStop stock made him an icon among Reddit-based traders during the recent meme-stock rally, and may have minted him a fortune — on paper at least.
